  ('dietitian-moex-00183', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關球蛋白（globular protein）正確折疊對生理功能影響的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["依據conformational entropy的理論，蛋白質處於entropy較低狀態時，較能進行正確的摺疊", "強酸或強鹼會破壞蛋白質分子間的鹽橋（salt bridges），導致蛋白質變性", "球蛋白的初級結構主要靠分子間的氫鍵和凡德瓦力（van der Waals interactions）維持", "含有leucine、isoleucine及phenylalanine側鏈，在水溶液中形成hydrophobic effect，以穩定蛋 白質的初級結構"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
